Definition: the use of heat to treat a disease or disorder
Example: heating pads or hot compresses or hot-water bottles are used to promote circulation in peripheral vascular disease or to relax tense muscles
Synonyms: therapy, the, use, of, heat, to, treat, a, disease, or, disorder, heating, pads, hot, compresses, hot-water, bottles, are, used, promote, circulation, in, peripheral, vascular, relax, tense, muscles
Category: noun.act
